---
/**
 * How It Works — three steps showing the voice-to-PDF flow.
 *
 * The argument: this isn't a digitised paper form. It's a different way of
 * working — speak the inspection instead of typing it, AI structures the
 * dictation into defect entries, inspector reviews and signs, PDF generated
 * on the device before leaving the site.
 *
 * Honesty note: Step 2 makes it clear that AI extraction is a capture aid
 * that produces a draft for the inspector to review. It does not make the
 * safety judgements — the inspector does. This matters for credibility
 * with RPII-certified readers and for professional/legal defensibility.
 *
 * Numbered steps with clear visual hierarchy. No icons-as-decoration; the
 * numbers ARE the visual. Restraint reads as confidence.
 */
---
<section class="border-b border-brand-100 bg-brand-50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
      <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-brand-700">
        How it works
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-brand-900 sm:text-4xl">
        From site visit to signed PDF, without the evening paperwork.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-700">
        Three steps. You run the inspection. InspectVoice handles the admin.
      </p>
    </div>
    <ol class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-5xl gap-10 sm:grid-cols-3 sm:gap-8">
      <li class="relative">
        <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-700 text-xl font-bold text-white">
          1
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-900">
          Walk the site, dictate findings
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
          Open the asset, hold the record button, speak naturally. &ldquo;Cracked
          weld on the swing frame, north-east corner, photo attached.&rdquo; The
          app captures voice and photos straight to the asset record — no
          typing, hands free for the inspection itself.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="relative">
        <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-700 text-xl font-bold text-white">
          2
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-900">
          AI drafts the defect entries
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
          Your dictation is transcribed and structured into draft defect
          entries — with suggested BS EN 1176 references, risk ratings, and
          recommended actions. You review and adjust each one before signing.
          The judgement is yours; the typing is done.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li class="relative">
        <div class="mb-5 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-700 text-xl font-bold text-white">
          3
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-900">
          Signed PDF on the device
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-slate-700">
          A polished, branded, BS EN 1176-aligned PDF is generated on your
          phone or tablet. Sign and send from the car park. No office
          evening, no second pass.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</section>
